==English==
===Etymology===
The idea of ''[[integer]]'' here is that the [[coefficient]] of the highest power <math>x^n</math> term is 1.
===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
# {{mathematics}} A number (real or complex) which is a solution to an equation of the form <math>x^n + a_1x^{n-1} + ... + a_n = 0</math> for some set of integers <math>a_1</math> through <math>a_n</math>.

